acceptGovernor().details: Accepts to become the next governor. Must only be called by the pending governor.

getCollFactor(address).details: Returns the collateral factor of the given token. Must be greater than zero.

getCollMaxAmount(address).details: Returns the collateral max amount of the given token. Must be greater than zero.

getKillBountyRate(address).details: Returns the kill bounty rate of the given token. Must be greater than zero.

getLiquidationLTV(address).details: Returns the liquidation LTV of the given token. Must be greater than zero.

getRiskLevel(address).details: Returns the risk level of the given token. Zero is the default value of all tokens.

getSafetyLTV(address).details: Returns the safety LTV of the given token. Must be greater than zero.

setCollInfos(address[],uint256[],uint256.details: Updates collateral information of the given tokens.

setPendingGovernor(address).details: Sets the next governor, which will be in effect when they accept.

setRiskConfigs(uint256[],(uint64,uint64,.details: Sets the risk configurations of the given levels.

setRiskLevels(address[],uint256[]).details: Sets the risk levels of the given tokens.
